[Kitwe is the 2nd largest city in terms of size and population in Zambia. With a population of 504 194 (2010 census provisional). Kitwe is one of the most developed commercial and industrial areas in the nation, alongside Ndola and Lusaka. It is located on the border with the Democratic Republic of Congo and can be found in the map of Zambia at: http://geology.com/world/zambia-satellite-image.shtml. - Mod.CP]

